al.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHV/110%2c%e9%87%8d%e4%b8%8a%e6%9b%b4%e4%ba%8c%2c81%2c20220209%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCHV,110,重上更二,81,20220209,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"重上更二","JNO":"81","JDATE":"20220209","JTITLE":"請求返還股權等"}